==Entities==
[[Phenomenon_9|Tulpaefication]] used to be a common way for entities to manifest due to the rich cultures that made up the level; however, many tulpaeified creatures are now extinct, serving no purpose for our style of quick documentation, so, for brevity, we will only document one instance of an important, extinct entity, with the others still roaming around the level in some capacity. If you wish to learn about the extinct tulpae, you can find information about them on their respective cultural databases.<br>
=== Khofners ===
<div class="status-container">
<div class="text-status">Status '''<'''</div>
