* Stepping into a cushy pile of snow in [[Level 1]] brings you here.
* Entering through an imposing, unbreakable door in Level ??? will bring you here.
* Staring at a painting, a mirror-like mirage that reflects the self, in [[Level 5]] will bring you here. 
